name: Leather Sequin Dress
description:
This Silver Metallic Leather Sequin Dress is made from silver metallic leather sequins with beading work on each sequin, all sequins are sewn on pure silk gorgette. The dress is a backless halter neck with a deep draped neck at the front.

Any Size Available.

name: Leather Sequin Hooded Jacket and Silk Jersey Polo Neck Dress
description:
This Silver Metallic Leather Sequin Hooded Jacket is made from silver metallic leather sequins with beading work on each sequin, all sequins are sewn on pure silk gorgette. The Jacket is long length with sequins all-over and a full sequined hood.

The Black Polo Neck Dress is made from pure silk jersey, it has a draped polo neck and long sleeves and long in length.

Any Sizes Available.

name: Leather Jacket With Draped Collar and High Waisted Leather Shorts
description:
This Off White Leather Jacket is made from real lamb nappa leather, the draped collar shows off the luxorious leather and suede side, as well as the cuff detail on the half sleeves. The jacket has a high collar with a silver metal ball zip fastening. Inside, the jacket is lined with pure black silk.

The Silver Gum Metallic shorts are made from real lamb nappa leather, they are short in length and are high waisted with a concealed zip fastening at the back The turn up detail at the bottom is made with real black lamb nappa suede. Inside, the shorts are lined with pure black silk.

All sizes available.

name: Leather Sequin Clutch Bag
description: This Leather Sequin Clutch Bag is made from silver metallic foil leather for the entire bag and leather sequins with beading work for the flap of the bag, all sequins are sewn on pure silk gorgette fabric. The bag is fully lined inside with pure black silk and consists of raw edged seams as a feature.
